CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

February 6, 2008

[Cite as 02/06/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-Ohio-381.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2007-2212. State ex rel. Martin v. Chief Inspector.

In Mandamus. On answer of respondent. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
